<li><a href="http://citeseer.ist.psu.edu/244698.html" class="external text" title="http://citeseer.ist.psu.edu/244698.html" rel="nofollow">Diebold, Francis X.; Hickman, Andrew; Inoue, Atsushi &amp; Schuermannm, Til (1996) "Converting 1-Day Volatility to h-Day Volatility: Scaling by sqrt(h) is Worse than You Think"</a></li>
